{"id": "1469922034661326950", "channel_id": "1439229898475438104", "type": 0, "author_id": "134247328876986369", "author_name": "aegisx", "author_bot": false, "content": "", "timestamp": "2026-02-08T05:05:22.894000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1439229898475438104", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Who Ryker's Designer pls come talk ?", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1469879211790569482", "channel_id": "1469879211790569482", "type": 0, "author_id": "1344504250784551014", "author_name": "syruponstrawberrycake", "author_bot": false, "content": "There are many issues with the current form of P-Dive, but this post will focus one: its insane difficulty.\n\nIn the current state of P-Dive, the recommended levels are very off. They might be accurate if it was about mob levels in arc2. However in arc2 you have access to Soulforge, which can give 25 levels worth of stats and an extra buff to the awakener's kit. There are some benefits to arc1 ruleset, but it doesn't nearly compensate for the lack of Soulforge.\n\nI really hope P-Dive can be tuned down a lot so non-whales can enjoy it as well.\n\n I'll put 3 comparisons of P-Dive mobs below.", "timestamp": "2026-02-08T02:15:13.126000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "agree", "emoji_id": "1400771815076528258", "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1469879211790569482", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Please nerf P-Dive", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1469879790097006672", "channel_id": "1469879211790569482", "type": 0, "author_id": "1344504250784551014", "author_name": "syruponstrawberrycake", "author_bot": false, "content": "Example #1: First mob stage in recommended lvl 60 P-Dive vs first mob stage in recommended lvl 74 H8-9. The two look very similar, and also Ch. 8 has a very powerful resonance effect.", "timestamp": "2026-02-08T02:17:31.005000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1469879790327697450", "filename": "ToSejOv.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1848828, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1469879211790569482/1469879790327697450/ToSejOv.png?ex=69cbd77b&is=69ca85fb&hm=5db9f971b7cc8b14d55e7e8aabc46af103632bb74d94742364b836afac75e77e&"}, {"id": "1469879790860501002", "filename": "X4qfbJg.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1852734, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1469879211790569482/1469879790860501002/X4qfbJg.png?ex=69cbd77b&is=69ca85fb&hm=3cb0185a947e29dc3dbe62d4f276448220fedd329cdf539934d1d20a9b4de9ae&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1469879211790569482", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Please nerf P-Dive", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1469880931992076514", "channel_id": "1469879211790569482", "type": 0, "author_id": "1344504250784551014", "author_name": "syruponstrawberrycake", "author_bot": false, "content": "Example #2: Elite mob in recommended lvl 80 P-Dive vs W3A5 Leigh (rec lvl 77 in arc2)\n\nI know you can't see damage intentions but these two have very similar effective HP amounts, but one is set in arc2 while the other is set in arc1. And this is just the elite in the stage.", "timestamp": "2026-02-08T02:22:03.254000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1469880932831068244", "filename": "TaVyuHI.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1830238, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1469879211790569482/1469880932831068244/TaVyuHI.png?ex=69cbd88b&is=69ca870b&hm=d56443fd99e4374717b01947814137bb205f26922020119afc4db979b1f736fc&"}, {"id": "1469880933665476649", "filename": "uahX1WW.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1937839, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1469879211790569482/1469880933665476649/uahX1WW.png?ex=69cbd88b&is=69ca870b&hm=d57c58330c27f0ad8c6d6c4a6535392767a9046167ebfea7139758b181590503&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1469879211790569482", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Please nerf P-Dive", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1469882474258628853", "channel_id": "1469879211790569482", "type": 0, "author_id": "1344504250784551014", "author_name": "syruponstrawberrycake", "author_bot": false, "content": "Example #3: Final boss in recommended lvl 80 P-Dive vs W4A5 protector (rec lvl 78 arc2)\n\nThe two have similar HP amounts, but the right is so much easier. On W4A5:\n\n#1: You get Soulforge buffs\n#2: You get access to 2 very powerful arc2 relics\n#3: Some of the HP gets shaved off from ancient embers", "timestamp": "2026-02-08T02:28:10.959000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1469882474426269868", "filename": "KTMwCTm.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1562500, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1469879211790569482/1469882474426269868/KTMwCTm.png?ex=69cbd9fa&is=69ca887a&hm=0f46ed117edfcd745a379b928d316a052da5e12495f386cae6c945b50da5fd01&"}, {"id": "1469882474862481642", "filename": "wO5tawb.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2338027, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1469879211790569482/1469882474862481642/wO5tawb.png?ex=69cbd9fb&is=69ca887b&hm=bfe32a8fb109b365d53481cd9b2ef1347216cafbe07963260fb06703823ed2a8&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1469879211790569482", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Please nerf P-Dive", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1469884839778848798", "channel_id": "1469879211790569482", "type": 0, "author_id": "184357317301501952", "author_name": "lumato", "author_bot": false, "content": "seems fine\n\narc2 rules are more restrictive", "timestamp": "2026-02-08T02:37:34.943000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1469879211790569482", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Please nerf P-Dive", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
